==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# small pieces of [[wood]] and [[twigs]] used to start a [[fire]].
#: ''Go and collect some '''kindling'''.''

====Usage notes====
'''Kindling''' refers to the second stage of building a fire: [[tinder]] is used to light kindling, which then lights the main fire.

